This project is a derivative work of opencode's webfetch tool,
which is part of the opencode project (https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode)
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

The following functions are derived from opencode's webfetch.ts:
  - acceptHeader, headers, mimeFrom, isImageAttachment, isTextualMime
  - isCloudflareChallenge, convert, extractTextFromHTML, convertHTMLToMarkdown
  - collectBoundedResponseBody
  - description text and constant definitions

Modifications from the original include:
  - Replaced Effect framework with Node.js native http + async/await
  - Added HTTP proxy support via CONNECT tunnel
  - Added MCP protocol layer (stdin/stdout JSON-RPC)
  - Converted TypeScript to JavaScript
  - Added redirect following with loop detection
